  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/4d26fda892f58f80f2c8287365bd33c5.avif?t=1756928433\" width=780 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">In Astronimo, up to four unfortunate employees of Hypergiant Inc. crash-land on a remote planet and must work together to escape. Armed with imagination, spare parts, and just enough optimism, you’ll build unstable machines, solve physics-based puzzles, and explore handcrafted worlds.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Whether you're bouncing across planets in a homemade catapult car or launching rockets with no pilot, Astronimo is all about joyful experimentation, co-op chaos, and interstellar fun.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/902dc0611912ad68171e4a446ef6726a.avif?t=1756928433\" width=780 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Snap together parts to create crazy machines - from rickety lifts to rocket-powered buses. Fail forward, break stuff, and try again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/a234db35dc7840c781d7c1ebc3736812.poster.avif?t=1756928433\" width=780 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/a234db35dc7840c781d7c1ebc3736812.webm?t=1756928433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/71e570c53d597154144e630da54fb769.avif?t=1756928433\" width=780 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Team up with friends online or on the couch. Work together… or accidentally launch each other into lava.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/58b9d9c83d55ec521d0eba314a2102a2.poster.avif?t=1756928433\" width=780 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/58b9d9c83d55ec521d0eba314a2102a2.webm?t=1756928433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/9811cbba5b1227cf530a94c1037b7240.avif?t=1756928433\" width=780 height=100 /></span>Explore bizarre planets like Turilla, Acara, Zaroth IV, and Nixnillon - each packed with puzzles, hazards, and secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/e51fb490e2f2f006ea278cc613009e61.poster.avif?t=1756928433\" width=780 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/e51fb490e2f2f006ea278cc613009e61.webm?t=1756928433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/d5e2598a3425e8a6314a7e570544dd74.avif?t=1756928433\" width=780 height=100 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Create your head, bling your suit, wave, dance, play music, or just be a dog in space. It’s weird out there - express yourself accordingly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/8d19979bdb5e87d6e5368fb75d0c65c0.poster.avif?t=1756928433\" width=780 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/8d19979bdb5e87d6e5368fb75d0c65c0.webm?t=1756928433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/ef2701b8d952e3852ea517db5aebf703.avif?t=1756928433\" width=780 height=100 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Create your own planets and levels with powerful, easy-to-learn world editing tools. Start with the tutorial to master the art of considered stupidity, then share your contraptions with the universe - or explore the wild inventions of others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/d5b7a00a831369e4a01bd1f48e1dfbcf.poster.avif?t=1756928433\" width=780 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/d5b7a00a831369e4a01bd1f48e1dfbcf.webm?t=1756928433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/9b6d0b95750c5134f2408bbb4f99ac59.avif?t=1756928433\" width=780 height=100 /></span>Each puzzle has endless solutions - just build what makes sense (or doesn’t). Gravity is optional. Sanity is not.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/bf97e8c0d5efae17a0b7b5742a5da84c.poster.avif?t=1756928433\" width=780 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808640/extras/bf97e8c0d5efae17a0b7b5742a5da84c.webm?t=1756928433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
